  "text": "Identification of genes differentially expressed between LN patients and LD controls was done using the framework proposed by McDavid et al. [CITATION_1] , as implemented by Seurat. P-values were corrected for multiple comparisons using the Benjamini-Hochberg method [CITATION_2] . DE analysis was performed separately for each cluster with at least 10 cells in both patient groups.",
